  "title": "Customer Sale Service (Joo Koon)",
  "description": "<p>Posting on behalf of our client at Joo Koon in Marine Safety Equipment</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>The role supports fire protection solutions provider at Joo Koon by delivering administrative, customer service, and sales operations assistance to ensure smooth coordination among teams, clients, and partners.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Enter and file data accurately to maintain organized records for sales and customer information</li><li>Respond promptly and clearly to customer enquiries to enhance satisfaction and support sales processes</li><li>Manage phone calls and correspondence including emails, letters, and packages to ensure effective communication</li><li>Organize and schedule appointments to support timely meetings and sales activities</li><li>Assist the sales team by preparing quotations and processing sales orders to facilitate smooth sales execution</li><li>Prepare and manage documentation for after-sales services to ensure proper follow-up and customer support</li><li>Maintain office cleanliness to provide a safe and professional work environment</li><li>Perform ad-hoc tasks as assigned to support team and operational needs</li></ul><p>Interested candidates are encouraged to apply.</p><p>Kita Solutions Pte Ltd<br />EA Licence No: 22C1420<br />Lim Kian Meng<br />R23113357</p>",
